:name:
Apotechary

:coretxt:
You know what medication is needed to cure disease.
This is used with \AbilityNameMedicine{}.
If someone has Reason or Vigor wound you can provide cure for it.
Decrease target wound by level of success and change its type to Instinct wound(if wound left is higher than 0).
If wound is left after this receiver of the cure buys themselves Key of Substance Abuse.


:cost:
1 from reason pool

:tags:
Ability
Medicine
